AVERMEDIA INFO said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 43.30% to NT$123,028,000 from NT$216,963,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            123,028          216,963    
YOY%             -43.30%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            671,950          969,218    
YOY%             -30.67% 
=================================================================
 